        java.util.TreeMap<java.time.OffsetDateTime,fr.ubo.fast.common.model.AggregatedObservationRecord> getData(java.lang.String name,
                                                                                                         java.util.List<fr.ubo.fast.common.model.AggregationType> aggregations,

                                                                                                         java.time.OffsetDateTime end_time,
                                                                                                         double interval,
                                                                                                         int values_number)
        Retrieve data for a specific time series and a list of aggregations over a given time range.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the measured variable linked to the time series.
        aggregations - List of requested aggregation types.
        start_time - Start time of the time window.
        end_time - End time of the time window.
        interval - Interval over which aggregations are calculated, expressed in seconds.
        values_number - Number of values (buckets) to return.
        Returns:
        Retrieved values with their timestamps.
